This extension is a quick fun game to play from your browser! There are more than 40 levels, powerups, upgrades and many cosmetic items to collect! 
This game also uses wacky physics and precise aiming to make sure you have to duck correctly aimed at the monsters! 
You can play this game especially in class, at home or even outside!
